cs.IR, cs.CL, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.SI 

This paper is about news recommendation, which is a subfield of information retrieval (IR) and natural language processing (NLP). Therefore, cs.IR and cs.CL are the most likely sub-categories. The paper also proposes a neural network model, which falls under the category of machine learning (ML). Thus, cs.LG and cs.AI are also likely sub-categories. Finally, the paper deals with personalized attention, which is a topic related to user modeling and recommendation systems. Therefore, cs.SI (social and information networks) is also a possible sub-category.
